NAME

    Perl::Critic::Plicease - Some Perl::Critic policies used by Plicease

VERSION

    version 0.02

DESCRIPTION

    The Perl::Critic::Policy::Plicease policies are a collection of
    Perl::Critic policies. They aren't grouped into a theme because some
    are application specific and you should review and include them only on
    a case by case basis.

AUTHOR

